# FragDenStaat Monitoring Cron Configuration
#
# This cron job runs the FragDenStaat monitoring script every 2 hours
# to check for new replies to FOI requests.
#
# Installation:
#   crontab -e
#   Then add the following line (adjust path if needed):
#
#   0 */2 * * * /home/david/german-protest-registrations/scripts/monitor.sh
#
# This will run at: 00:00, 02:00, 04:00, 06:00, 08:00, 10:00, 12:00, 14:00, 16:00, 18:00, 20:00, 22:00
#
# Alternative schedules:
#   - Every hour:        0 * * * * /home/david/german-protest-registrations/scripts/monitor.sh
#   - Every 4 hours:     0 */4 * * * /home/david/german-protest-registrations/scripts/monitor.sh
#   - Business hours:    0 8-18/2 * * 1-5 /home/david/german-protest-registrations/scripts/monitor.sh
#   - Twice daily:       0 8,20 * * * /home/david/german-protest-registrations/scripts/monitor.sh
#

# Run every 2 hours
0 */2 * * * /home/david/german-protest-registrations/scripts/monitor.sh
